window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Hidden deep within the Castle of Ascendance are other Creation Mages.</b></p> <p>If I'm to save the Universal Magic, I need to find them. What I need to do with them isn't exactly fit for public consumption, but it's fundamental to who I am as a Creation Mage.</p> <p>I just have to slip into the castle, disguised as a noble, and snatch four other Creation Mages. All while avoiding the eyes of the Queen and the Arcane Council.</p> <p>Easy, right?</p>"; 
